ğŸ§ . What will you do if there is a broken build in your Jenkins project?
  Check the console output for errors, identify any missed changes, and attempt to replicate and fix the issue locally.

Git/SCM issues â€“ wrong repo, branch, or authentication failure
fatal: Authentication failed

Jenkinsfile errors â€“ syntax or pipeline configuration mistakes
WorkflowScript: 15: Expected a step

Agent/server issues â€“ agent offline, low memory, disk full
Agent went offline during the build

Tool issues â€“ Maven, Java, Docker not installed or wrong version
mvn: command not found

Environment issues â€“ missing environment variables or credentials
ERROR: Could not find credentials with ID 'aws-creds'

Timeouts or resource limits â€“ build exceeded time or memory limits
script returned exit code 137

