ğŸ§ . How to configure Docker in Jenkins?
  Install Docker plugin, configure Docker settings in "Manage Jenkins", and use Docker commands in pipeline scripts.
   A) Install Docker on Jenkins Server
  (B) Give Jenkins user permission to use Docker
  (C) Install Docker plugins (optional)
  (D) Configure Jenkins pipeline to use Docker

