 Configure Pipeline to use Git

Scroll down to Pipeline section
Definition: select Pipeline script from SCM
SCM: select Git
Repository URL: enter your repo, e.g.:
https://github.com/username/repo.git
Branch: enter the branch, e.g., main
Script Path: enter the Jenkinsfile path (default is Jenkinsfile)
If your Jenkinsfile is inside a folder like ci/, use ci/Jenkinsfile

